item.title: PF issue
item.dc:creator: @Meeper98 Meeper98
item.description:
@Meeper98 wrote:

…YOU DONT PORTFORWARD WITH UTURRENT, when you portforward it will ask for your default gateway ip adress, “192.168.1.” will allready be set, then you fill in the last ## which is 111 as from what i saw in the picture, the ip their connecting to is your ip so that has little to do with portforwarding. Im not saying for them to connect to 192.168.1.1, thats just ur gateway ip which u change the last number to which in ur case is the #111
